{"tid":327822,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"牠走了，我係一個壞主人（長內容）","createTime":"2017-07-19T05:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T15:25:26.000Z","uid":100088,"like":89,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd5f9912f54d14cb215865d32e1a3c62e274068","tid":327822,"uid":100088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:37:04.000Z","msg":"純舒發，行文粗糙，勿見怪<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前，佢確診左有淋巴癌<br />\n對於狗黎講，好常見，但佢只有4歲，可能我尋日仲諗緊下年畢業帶唔帶到佢去影相，佢老既時候賴屎賴尿仲俾唔俾佢上床訓好呢⋯呢d種種既努想同憂慮，係一瞬間全部無曬<br />\n「你地盡量陪佢多d」<br />\n「it is not about the 時間, but the quality 」<br />\n好多人都咁講，我都好明白，但每當我摸到佢下巴兩粒手指咁大既腫留，我就唔敢再掂佢。<br />\n我好怕失去佢，好怕無左佢，但我愈怕，我愈無辦法接近佢。可能我認為，小小既疏離，可以減輕佢走個日所帶俾我既痛楚⋯<br />\n直到有一日，佢開始收埋自己，唔去有人既地方，唔食野，唔飲野。我終於開始心急。<br />\n「無事架無事架」我上去摸住佢咁講，先發現佢已經瘦左好多，曾經俾人笑肥婆既佢，今日竟然可以摸到佢既骨頭，下巴既腫留已經連成一串，有如頸鍊一樣。<br />\n<br />\n曾經我想為佢做化療，覺得痛唔痛苦都好，多一日就一日。但到左呢刻，我覺得佢可以訓係我大臂到離開先係最好⋯<br />\n<br />\n直至近兩日，佢失禁，想必都知道情況已經接近最壞，大家都已經諗好曬安樂死同善終既野。<br />\n「你覺得o唔ok?」阿爸問我。我盤坐係隻狗面前，我無辦法哼出半粒字。<br />\n「咁就約左今日5點」語氣需輕，但我明白阿爸既心情都好沈重，由完全唔鍾意動物，到幾乎一手一腳打理佢既，始終都係佢。就好似三代人咁，我（爸爸）成日都唔想寵隻狗（個女），但阿爸（爺爺）永遠都要塞最好既俾佢⋯<br />\n帶著不捨既心情，阿爸都要番工，我亦唔忍心再望住佢，想去游水散下心。<br />\n<br />\n點知又會咁岩，今日係例行洗池既日子，本來我都打算做其他野，但最後我都決定左番去。<br />\n<br />\n屋企，只剩下我一個。<br />\n後腳都站唔穩既佢，緩緩走到我面前，想爬到我的大腿上面休息，但佢實在太虛弱，無我既輔助連爬上黎既能力都無。<br />\n佢就係咁，係我身上面喘氣。<br />\n自從佢有左癌症，加上天氣熱，佢都好小再訓係我到，但今次就足足訓左半個鍾。<br />\n「你安心走啦，無人會怪你。」我控制唔到我既淚水，我甚至睇唔清近在腳前既佢，我講既野就好似機械人咁，毫無意識咁重覆地講。<br />\n我唔知佢明唔明，但到左呢刻。我仲可以點⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我慢慢將佢放係地下，去左廁所。出番黎佢已經入左房，佢企到直一直咁望住我同佢一齊訓既床，究竟佢諗緊咩？<br />\n<br />\n我知時間不多，都跟著入去，拎起結他，為佢唱出左第一次，獻俾佢既「小白」<br />\n「離開世界，如果兩眼很重」平時毫無難度的一句，如今我竟然唱不出來。但我忍著淚水，以最溫柔的節奏，把歌唱了半首。<br />\n「我只有2個願望，希望你可以為我做⋯」我喊曬咁講：「1係希望你可以自己決定幾時走，唔好由我去決定⋯」佢繼續喘氣，貼著我的腳板。「2係希望你聽得明我講咩，半⋯唔使，哪怕只係一分鍾都好」之後我就開始講「我地全家都好愛你⋯」夾帶著哭聲，我幾乎無法完整講出心聲，但我有一種感覺，我所祈求既呢一分鍾，就係最後既一分鍾。<br />\n「你走左無人會怪你，我好後悔呢段時間無陪你⋯我好驚，驚去摸你，驚去陪你，驚見到你⋯因為我接受唔到失去你⋯」我知我講再多，佢都未必會原諒我，但我只希望佢接收到呢番說話。<br />\n「我地真係好愛你」<br />\n<br />\n話畢，我想為佢唱奏埋下半段既小白，但佢突然開始全身向後抽搐，我即刻放低部結他，跪係到就抱住佢，一路叫佢個名。接著、佢就嘔了一堆黃膽水，同時又失禁尿得一地都係。我不停叫佢唔好走，唔好走啊！但明明上一秒，最想佢離開既，就係我。<br />\n人，總是矛盾。人，總是失去了才珍惜。<br />\n無論過幾多千年，這也是不變的道理。<br />\n<br />\n我抬起佢個頭，舌頭都吐出來了，雙眼睜大，但更明顯的是，哪煩人的喘氣聲，已經不見了⋯永遠也沒有了⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生命，就係咁脆弱既一件事。<br />\n我很心痛，因為我係一個壞主人，我係盡責咁陪佢，我自私地為左減少自己既痛楚，而疏遠左佢。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我只想佢唔好怪我，只想佢到最後一刻，都唔好忘記我地所有人，都好愛佢⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/133649_2f22307f1d96e0c5588247ab93e955ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F133649_2f22307f1d96e0c5588247ab93e955ce.jpg&h=ccf81a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再見了"},{"pid":"9aeeca1e176d13e59506a5a7aca445512299be69","tid":327822,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係街睇到一半已經feel到好sad<br />\nlm返屋企再睇"},{"pid":"86c86e066427ce9a0273b7ae3e6250569d76e9d7","tid":327822,"uid":127269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809a634dd21d303ab644389f266fff525c4936d3","tid":327822,"uid":12319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e01f3cf1a24bbffe2d660ef2de62ed0cf516a72","tid":327822,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:55:13.000Z","msg":"節哀順變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc8b8a3b0fd7d04d4edc241c3a46002a96d763d","tid":327822,"uid":62084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717554155e431ec6f420fe1c6b733756f3d81e6f","tid":327822,"uid":71517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3f21662c8779bf049dcebe5e7c9aeb896d2efa","tid":327822,"uid":55830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8774438258a0d291c4a1a2e319e25d9bee470dc0","tid":327822,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cc0496ebff109ddac196d789241ab26d237b26","tid":327822,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3a8af53e22d32c93e2829c7458e46b98a603af","tid":327822,"uid":50793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155b4dc91a21999f405522f22731ae821e188d36","tid":327822,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"樓主個名咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好奇一問"},{"pid":"93e209530259e41d0ef5fc1b0737f9bc3a59e9bd","tid":327822,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ec6cd9d7640de82bce71caa46823ab11fc9861","tid":327822,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保重"},{"pid":"53a4e925671830c316785e2390a4f73e680babb8","tid":327822,"uid":57384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d424f0885af471577ad8b72eb67e28a7454be960","tid":327822,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"聽你咁講 佢應該走得唔係幾舒服..<br />\nbtw rip 我都好驚我果兩隻貓離開我"},{"pid":"b108498a33185335ff89ba01d1e2d9e569565fdb","tid":327822,"uid":1287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39b00ed21efdfd566f3e781af1798ccee57d23a","tid":327822,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"一入黎成堆洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f98601651afbc99b73062812aefa36b1676464e","tid":327822,"uid":100088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽你咁講 佢應該走得唔係幾舒服..<br />\nbtw rip 我都好驚我果兩隻貓離開我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情況未到最壞，因為最壞可能會入院吊鹽水，真係生活都不能自理個種<br />\n<br />\n佢到最後仲識走去個盤到大小便<br />\n<br />\n不過佢辛苦就一定，但最後我都叫陪到佢最後一秒⋯"},{"pid":"f2d519067c3f79df95a8b5ca3717f70a3dbb8e62","tid":327822,"uid":67283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:51:26.000Z","msg":"屌睇到流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365e3e05a7682d2e3ebd3919951fa9237f53491c","tid":327822,"uid":100088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"大家有養寵物一定要好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ab4479f791060177c71b34bd6f665803f7c9c5","tid":327822,"uid":1495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢會喺彩虹橋等你，節哀順變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7229d97c383e5648aa87a8a703d77c90f97c480","tid":327822,"uid":21526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"樓主遲啲會係彩虹橋同小白遇返架喇.. <br />\n睇完之後好心up<br />\n我會更加好好珍惜我隻狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227b2327596f4ece1f0a1855cb212f14619ae96f","tid":327822,"uid":49597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"樓主狗狗遇到你係佢呢一生最大既福氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個好主人<br />\n唔好太傷心 記住你同佢獨有既回憶"},{"pid":"c0c45288a3269033d5ea094b3a553d9cbd15a809","tid":327822,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:31:27.000Z","msg":"我果隻6歲,都係淋巴,做左化療4個月都零進展,一停化療一星期就食唔到野"},{"pid":"02579a1b2a38312ed82ffa228f0ca2cd45eeffb5","tid":327822,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果隻6歲,都係淋巴,做左化療4個月都零進展,一停化療一星期就食唔到野</blockquote><br />\n不過我果陣係簽紙畀佢走,我比你好運係佢唔洗死得咁辛苦又嘔又屙<br />\n針都未打完,唔洗3秒對眼已經冇晒神"},{"pid":"503b4ff9394664a23b9ca8dd882076bb6863d338","tid":327822,"uid":100088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果隻6歲,都係淋巴,做左化療4個月都零進展,一停化療一星期就食唔到野</blockquote><br />\n不過我果陣係簽紙畀佢走,我比你好運係佢唔洗死得咁辛苦又嘔又屙<br />\n針都未打完,唔洗3秒對眼已經冇晒神</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對我地黎講，佢咁走都係件好事，因為醫生講過有機會又嘔又抽幾個鐘都走唔到<br />\n但當時佢只係經歷左10秒左右，算短<br />\n<br />\n對我阿爸黎講，或者屋企黎講，唔使成為主宰佢生死既人，都係件好事<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，祝所有小寵物都可以開心陪主人<br />\n而已經離開左既，都永在主人心中<br />\n<br />\n唯有永不忘記呢種痛同情，先可以確定佢真正存在過"},{"pid":"f10dbec112177a2f00c209465b9b820e14ad9d94","tid":327822,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"Take care...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a67d5e21636d5c4906ab65cdd3de6ab2b85c971","tid":327822,"uid":67096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"睇到喊左 我諗我主人走左 我唔會再養 真係好痛 我唔會接受到 唔敢想像<br />\n我愛佢仲多過愛自己爸爸媽媽 我係咪痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa17102f495fe1b0881685f8c67ec7db5c90a901","tid":327822,"uid":100088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到喊左 我諗我主人走左 我唔會再養 真係好痛 我唔會接受到 唔敢想像<br />\n我愛佢仲多過愛自己爸爸媽媽 我係咪痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為寵物有種好特別既感覺，就係「佢地永遠都似小朋友，需要你，你亦需要佢」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你養既係咩寵物<br />\n但我有朋友都經歷過狗狗既離開好多次，而佢地會係每一隻走之前都帶一隻新既番屋企做過渡<br />\n<br />\n可能有人覺得好殘忍，原本隻狗一定好傷心<br />\n但朋友話，佢睇得出隻狗見到有新狗入伙之後，係安穩左好多開心左，好似知道會有新一任既去保護主人一樣，放心曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa930f9bb8af1461d408b641d57f256f9270a0c9","tid":327822,"uid":76181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"節哀順變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdd7999f8204a54ab86d20f1f5e5b51db05bf33","tid":327822,"uid":69674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:39:15.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"93f82dba9d7628f3451b8802e558283b3d37865d","tid":327822,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddfb2f8d701d6c0c08e1e6ed3a2cacb76a8784a","tid":327822,"uid":75528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfa345943c8103431a7e2fe557cf90e6e3bd713","tid":327822,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到喊"},{"pid":"5838e4dc852c134fc39c23e060c81872679049ab","tid":327822,"uid":350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 八哥好可愛的<br />\n又好有性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我細個都有隻..又係好痴我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988ac09238b13b8ad3fc9c9c674f8c684f1d7dd5","tid":327822,"uid":43171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:37:38.000Z","msg":"睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都養緊八哥"},{"pid":"1a7938f8d4a2edc5df4d61c0f75d50547ab6fe90","tid":327822,"uid":24207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"諗起我隻狗狗<br />\n我同佢講：如果你覺得好辛苦你就走啦，唔好再勉強自己，我會好心痛㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住一個鐘後，佢就瞓住覺咁走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b9db651e575b17693a4e3f8ead5d4aab16b410","tid":327822,"uid":108660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"樓主Take care!睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢會係彩虹轎等你架！"},{"pid":"2280c7b887046c4b40c63711c1bfca5506d7948d","tid":327822,"uid":124163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"你有呢個心，好好架啦<br />\n<br />\n佢會感覺到你係點對佢，至少佢最後都係有你陪住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a10038f4cfa2a716a8723859c5315e07e8ba03d","tid":327822,"uid":94512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T20:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頂住"},{"pid":"6eb8d89fdd9411e8af79dd4f79c83165b3af752e","tid":327822,"uid":36942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T23:32:36.000Z","msg":"你唔係壞主人，生老病死，無人控制到，佢病左生命短左，無人想架，佢都唔想。佢有你陪住走，聽住你講全家都好愛佢，佢會好安慰架。你知嗎，寵物既使命係俾愛我地，我地俾番愛佢，你地已經係好好既主人。佢絕對會明白你心意架，佢會返黎睇你地，有時會繼續同你地住添。唔好太傷心，寵物黎我地屋企係令我地開心，你太傷心佢會擔心你，唔捨得投胎架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7461e6245e9e001c2bd66719af6c78ff98eb1bbb","tid":327822,"uid":120723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"係地鐵睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aab44cb36ade46da263f474f7b75d245ac4bb48","tid":327822,"uid":120723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢一定收到你既心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9053a4ff67cc56fc7cd97aa8a77bc82721bb7503","tid":327822,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"89cd881c40dc83910c492ef68c633a1521791efb","tid":327822,"uid":63291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"我都經歷過兩隻貓嘅離開<br />\n<br />\n依家望返轉頭，寵物嘅離開係必然，冇得避免。<br />\n最重要嘅珍惜佢仲在生嘅每一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b524d9d64e4abc968cd8a7c0bd829c5cd19f10cf","tid":327822,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ec14fbc303baeaf963d2f77fd16e255a2accfa","tid":327822,"uid":72205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"睇完你個post...我喊左5分鐘都停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以決定番黎留個言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbaaf1b181f0eb483c9db011ef6f21887f20c7f","tid":327822,"uid":105668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"屌睇到流哂馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾年前細個唔識諗 冇好好照顧自己既寵物 呀媽唯有將佢地俾左人 唔知佢地哩家生活得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到哩家每次諗番起都好後悔好後悔 間唔中仲會發夢佢地番番黎搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好掛住佢地 佢地真係好乖好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4343bbb3d3df40a2ceb1ab707f095239c41c0b43","tid":327822,"uid":122895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}